parameters: \n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiThis place is like my old bachelor pad, \|but nicer.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiWe need you to lay down \.\.and stop moving!
\n<\c[6]Dee\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYeah,\.\. we're on a quest to save every soul,\.\. and right all wrongs!
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiIf you think there's any hope of \|\.\."saving"\.\.\. my poor,\.\.\.\.\. fragile little soul...
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiWe're just here to clobber you a fuckton of times,\|\| over the head!
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou've finally found me, \|\.\.and you've decided to join the others in killing me.
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou really pulled the wool over my fuckin' eyes,\|\.\. y'know that?
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI don't know what you did to my head,\|\.\. but...
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI can't forgive you for what you've done.
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiFor what you've done to me, \|\.\.and everyone else.
\n<\c[30]Dave\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiThis has been a long time comin'.
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI couldn't have done it without you.
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou look about as human as the rabbit suit that you used to wear.
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI never figured out exactly what you were, \|\|\.\.\.but a human,\|\. you are not.
\fiThis is the end of your pathetic "legacy", \c[27]Henry\c[0].
\fiThis is the end of your pathetic "legacy", \c[27]Henry\c[0].

\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiA gigantic,\| soulless,\| orange infant, \|\.\.2 rotary phones, \|\|a sock puppet,\| the purple muppet-baby that the world tried to forget, \|\|\|\.\.and the Dog of Christmas Past.
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI'm \c[27]Dr Henry Miller\c[0],\|\| and I'm going to teach you all what you failed to learn \|\|\|\c[10]the first time I slaughtered each and every one of you.
\n<\c[27]Henry\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fi\c[10]I have been sealed here for an epoch.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiWe showed that pink \.\.h-\.h-\.h-\.\{HECKER\.\} who was boss, \.\.didn't we?

\.\.\.
Does that mean it's time for us to go?

\|
I think we all have someone to thank.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI never really knew you all that well.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI guess I've never really known anyone all that well...
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiHere I am,\.\. workin' a dead-end pizza job, \.\.\.my head is a phone,\.\. etc, \.etc...
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiNext thing I know, \.\.\.you show up, \.\.and it all comes crashing down.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiMy wife was a lie, \.\.my life was a lie,\.\.\. my kids were probably robots or whatever.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiEven though you couldn't fix yourself, \|you fixed me.
\n<\c[10]Steven\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI hope you'll somehow be able to join us.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiAlright, \.\.time for the second phone-headed guy in your life to do this.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiLook, \.\.bro, \.\.you know I've never been any good at goodbyes.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiWasn't any good the first time, \|or the second time, \.\.\.and this is no exception.

\|
If there's one thing I can say about you, \|it's that you don't give up.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou come back to people, \|even when they don't necessarily deserve it.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou vowed to find her,\.\.\. and you did.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiNone of this would've been possible if it weren't for you.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI'm glad you saved me,\| but frankly, \.\.I would've given up my salvation in exchange for hers.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiAnd yet, \.\.we both get to go together.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiThis is the first time we've really been together in this era.

\|
The first time since Mom and Dad died...
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI'm sorry I left you two alone.

\|
And\.\. I'm so sorry for blaming you for what happened.
\n<\c[10]Peter\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiThanks for never giving up on her.
\fiI hope I can join you both soon.
\fiI hope I can join you both soon.
\n<\c[6]Dee\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiYou've made your fair share of mistakes, \.\.\.but...
\n<\c[6]Dee\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI've never met anyone willing to go as far as you have, \|\.\.just to right their own wrongs.
\n<\c[6]Dee\c[0]>\c[0]<Wordwrap>\fiI'm so glad that you found me.
I'll join you all soon, I just know it. \}[Bitter lie]
